headline.print_headline: Date-Krumm Loses to Teenager at Australian Open
headline.main: Date-Krumm Loses to Teenager at Australian Open

lead_paragraph: Kimiko Date-Krumm is used to questions about retirement but still has no answer. For now, she's content to continue the "miracle" of playing professional tennis at age 43.
